   - ExitPlanMode rejection: "Yes, and auto-accept. ALSO, add in CLAUDE.md the new architecture (arget file struct + dependency graph) in a 'Front end' part"
   - "continue / retry" (after caveman-mode reminder)

7. Pending Tasks:
