   - **Rewrite `app/static/index.html`**: remove 388-line inline `<style>` block, remove 5 CDN script tags + 5 local script tags, add single `<script type="module" src="/src/app.js"></script>`. Keep all DOM structure (topbar, sidebar, canvas-wrap, panel, forms, menus, auth-overlay).
